Use relatedSamplingFeature to relate samples to parent and sibling samples. For example: 1. relate mineral grains to an enclosing polished mount, 2. relate burn spots to a parent mineral grain, 3. relate a crushed powder sample to its parent rock specimen, 4. relate sample splits to parent samples, 5. relate a specimen to its parent borehole, 6. relate a water sample to its parent water bore
